<Speech gate:gateId="107081" majorType="ParlmemberSpeech"><SpeechStart gate:gateId="106385" majorType="ParlmemberSpeechStart"><Parlmember gate:gateId="105295" majorType="speaker">ΦΩΤΕΙΝΗ ΠΙΠΙΛΗ</Parlmember>:</SpeechStart> Κύριε Πρόεδρε, θα ήθελα τον λόγο.</Speech>
<Speech gate:gateId="107082" majorType="ParlmemberSpeech"><Parlmember gate:gateId="105296" majorType="speaker">ΠΡΟΕΔΡΕΥΩΝ</Parlmember> (<Speech gate:gateId="107548" majorType="ChairmanSpeech"><SpeechStart gate:gateId="105965" majorType="ChairmanSpeechStart"><Chairman gate:gateId="105762" majorType="speaker">Γεώργιος Καλαντζής</Chairman>):</SpeechStart> Είστε παλαιά, έμπειρη και ξέρετε ότι δεν έχετε τον λόγο.</Speech></Speech> 
